            <scopecontent>
                <p>Papers of Luigi (Louis) Costa including certificate of US citizenship, 1886;
                    continuous discharge book. signed by the captain of the Port of Genoa; letters
                    of recommendation from employers at various firms, 1887-1918; a bill of sale for
                    1/16 share in the bark Julia; payroll and disbursements for ships captained by
                    Costa; correspondence and letters of appointment; accounts, bills, and receipts;
                    a will and insurance policy of Louis Giliasso, 1916; issues of the Crow's Nest,
                    1920 and 1930; annual reports of the Pennsylvania Seamens' Friend, 1915 and
                    1920; a small number of documents related to Costa's management of the Sailor's
                    Home; and a few miscellaneous other items.</p>
            </scopecontent>

